<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.1.3">
<l>kāmuṟṟa kaiyaṟavō ṭellē yirāppaka</l>
<l>ṉīmuṟṟak kaṇṭuyilāy neñcuruki yēṅkutiyā</l>
<l>ṟīmuṟṟat teṉṉilaṅkai yūṭṭiṉāṉ ṟāṇayanta</l>
<l>yāmuṟṟa tuṟṟāyō vāḻi kaṉaikaṭalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>With helplessness out of desire you will lament all day [and] night,</l>
<l>[your] eyes totally without sleep, heart melting.</l>
<l>Do you have what we had, who longed for the feet of him who fed</l>
<l>southern Lanka totally to the fire – oh sounding sea?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
